@92506 = ~Wand of Charm Person or Mammal~
@92507 = ~This wand will charm any single person† or animal‡ when activated; if the target fails <PRO_HISHER> saving throw vs. Wand at +2 bonus, <PRO_HESHE> regards the caster as a trusted friend and ally to be heeded and protected. The wielder may give <PRO_HIMHER> orders, and the charmed creature will carry them out as quickly as possible. <PRO_HESHE> will also gladly provide valuable information to <PRO_HISHER> new ally.

