//Minor Spell Deflection
@93034 = ~Wand of Minor Spell Deflection~
@93035 = ~This wand causes any spells cast against the wielder to be absorbed and consumed. This affects a total of 6 spell levels, but having 1 level left of protection means a 1st level spell would get absorbed, as well as a 4th level spell. Spells greater than 4th level will not be affected. This spell will not protect the wielder from a dispel magic. However, it will not be affected by a dispel magic, either.

This spell absorbs spells cast from scrolls and innate spell-like abilities, but will not protect against area effect spells that are not centered directly upon the wielder (such as Fireball), or stationary area effect spells (such as Cloudkill and Stinking Cloud).

