//Halt Undead
@93044 = ~Wand of Halt Undead~
@93045 = ~Upon activation, this wand stops undead creatures in their place for the duration of the spell. The effect is centered on the victim selected by the wielder. Any undead creatures within 5 feet of the target are also affected. Those who succeed at a saving throw vs. wand at -2 are totally unaffected by the spell.

