//Melf's Minute Meteors
@93046 = ~Wand of Melf's Minute Meteors~
@93047 = ~Upon activation, this wand creates %magnitude% small globes of fire, which, when thrown, burst upon impact and inflict 1d4 points of piercing damage plus 2d4 points of fire damage to the creature struck. The wielder gains a +5 bonus to hit with the missiles, and each meteor is considered to be of +2 enchantment to determine what it can hit. The wielder may discharge up to five missiles per round.

