//Dispel Magic
@93048 = ~Wand of Dispel Magic~
@93049 = ~With targeting this wand, it removes magical effects upon any enemies within the area of effect. This includes effects from spells, potions, and certain magical items such as wands. It does not, however, affect enchanted magical items or spell protections such as Spell Deflection. While this spell dispels the individual effects of Grease, Web, Stinking Cloud, and other such spells, it does not dispel the area of effect. Magic resistance does not affect this spell.

The chance of the dispel succeeding is determined by the caster level of wand (%caster_level%) and the level of the magic being dispelled. The base chance of successfully dispelling is 50%. For every caster level that Dispel Magic is above the level of the magic it is trying to dispel, its chance of success increases by 5%. For every caster level that Dispel Magic is below the level of the magic it attempts to dispel, its chance of success decreases by 10%. However, despite the difference in levels, there is always at least a 1% chance of success or failure. Thus, if Dispel Magic is 10 caster levels higher than the magic it is trying to dispel, there is only a 1% chance of failure. Similarly if the caster level is 4 levels lower than the magic it is trying to dispel, there is only a 10% chance of success. Intuitively, this spell is almost useless if the level of the magic attempted to dispel is 5 or more levels higher than the wand's caster level.

STATISTICS:

Charge abilities:
– Dispel Magic
  – Dispells magical effects
  School: Abjuration
  Range: Long
  Duration: Instant
  Area of Effect: 20' radius
  Saving Throw: None

Requires:
 9 Intelligence

Weight: 1~


//Icelance
