@93514 = ~Wand of Call Lightning~
@93515 = ~When this wand is activated in an outdoor area, it will call down one 30-foot-long vertical bolt of lightning per round. The lightning will strike first at the target of the spell, dealing 6d6 points of electrical damage, with a successful save vs. breath at -2 reducing this to half. For the remainder of the storm's duration, the bolts will strike out randomly at the enemies of the wielder.

