@93539 = ~Once activated, this wand calls up unholy power to smite his enemies. The power takes the form of a chilling, cloying miasma of darkness. Opponents within the spell's area of effect take %magnitude%d4 points of magic damage, with a successful saving throw vs. wand for half. If the victim fails his save, then he will also receive a -2 penalty on his attack rolls and saving throws for 4 rounds.

